node.text: Welcome to the launch of the all new 2022 @cyclesdevinci Spartan enduro mountain bike! Watch now as @neildonoghue and @doddstar1979 check out all the details before taking it for a ride on the rough and fast trails of the Forest of Dean. Neil also talks to @greg_callaghan of @devinciglobalracing  before we find out about the design and development of the bike at Devinci Headquarters in Quebec, Canada.

node.text:
The @bluegrass_eagle @world_enduro @finaleoutdoorregion presented by @vittoriatires has reached its conclusion! Racers have been battling it out all day long on the dusty hillsides of the Italian Riviera, vying for valuable metres and seconds which will translate to points in a historically tight overall battle.
